Quick setup for VIM
-------------------
Add /usr/local/vim/vim74 to your runtime path, e.g.:
  :set rtp+=/usr/local/vim/vim74

Quick setup for EMACS
-------------------
Add /usr/local/share/emacs/site-lisp to your runtime path, e.g.:
  (add-to-list 'load-path "/usr/local/share/emacs/site-lisp")
  (require 'merlin)
Then issue M-x merlin-mode in a ML buffer.

Take a look at https://github.com/the-lambda-church/merlin for more information.
